## Where Public Docs Live

| Folder | Content area |
|--------|-------------|
| `docs/public/_general/` | Getting started guides |
| `docs/public/administration/` | Account, users, security |
| `docs/public/api/` | REST API |
| `docs/public/data-migration/` | Scorecard, mapping, SQL |
| `docs/public/dictionary/` | Objects, fields, tracking |
| `docs/public/erd/` | Entity relationship diagrams |
| `docs/public/integrations/<partner>/` | Partner-specific |
| `docs/public/metrics/` | Glossary, alias, AI analyst |
| `docs/public/reports-and-dashboards-datatools/` | Reports, dashboards |

---

## PR Checklist

Include in every user story PR:

- [ ] **Internal doc:** Created or updated `docs/features/` entry (or noted "N/A — task/bug")
- [ ] **Public doc evaluated:** New, updated, or not needed — state which
- [ ] If public doc created/updated: follows datatools-pro-docs skill quality checklist
- [ ] Related docs cross-linked
